## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d8ebb-102">Use un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> acción con un <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> o <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> para detener interactivamente un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ebb-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> action with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to interactively stop a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d8ebb-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> solo afecta a un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> cuando está activo (después de la <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> inicia).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ebb-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d8ebb-104">Detener los desencadenadores de guión gráfico la <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> y <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> eventos, pero no el <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> eventos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ebb-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d8ebb-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> no hace referencia a un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directamente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ebb-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d8ebb-106">En su lugar, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> debe hacer referencia a la <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> de la <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> que controla el <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ebb-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d8ebb-107">Vea [Cómo: utilizar desencadenadores de eventos para controlar un guión gráfico después de que se inicia](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) para obtener un ejemplo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ebb-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
